[normal]Written evidence submitted by Mr Gary Powell[bold]Further submission to the CLG Commit[bold]t[bold]ee in respect of its inquiry into the work of the Local Government Ombudsman.[bold]This submission is a response to the following request from the Clerk of the Communities and Local Government Committee, received on 6 
